## Getting started

```bash
{{packageManager}} install
cp .env.example .env
{{packageManager}} run dev
```

The server starts on `http://localhost:${PORT}` (default `3000`).

## Scripts

- `{{packageManager}} run dev` — start in watch mode (tsx)
- `{{packageManager}} run build` — compile to `dist/`
- `{{packageManager}} run start` — run the compiled server
- `{{packageManager}} run typecheck` — strict type check

## Architecture

```
src/
  config/     environment validation
  plugins/    autoloaded, app-wide plugins (security, db, …)
  modules/    feature slices; every *.route.ts is autoloaded
  app.ts      builds the Fastify instance
  server.ts   process entrypoint + graceful shutdown
```

Plugins in `src/plugins` and any `*.route.ts` in `src/modules` are registered
automatically — add a file and it wires itself in.

